node.text:
(Part 2/2)

Tova and her family have been living in a tiny cabin in the Swedish forest for 8 years. Here’s a home tour! For more videos, I highly recommend you check out their YouTube channel (linked below).

Link to original video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TWfl990NHoM

Link to YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxl_etcRcrFMYul-5N0u1Mg

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ✨ Cabin Love is Love ✨ on August 17, 2021 tagging @visitnorway, @torhveem, @norge, @cabinlove, @lofoten, and @lofotenislands. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
Something about this little shack, the trodden path, the sea. It makes me think of the start of summer and salt and strawberries. Of that passage you sent and the last hot days before autumn and sweaters, fires and tea. 

Swipe for the passage by Franny Choi from “Soft Sciences Poems.” Image by @torhveem in the near to nowhere of Lofoten, Norway. 🇳🇴 #cabinlove #shacksandthesea #farfaraway #norway #lofoten #lonelyhouses
